n-menu-item-2" href="/loi/radiographics" tabindex="" class="nav-link text-small-bold">All Issues</a></li><li class="nav-item pr-xl-24"><div class="dropdown"><a id="publication-menu-item-3" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-small-bold">Collections</a><div aria-labelledby="publication-menu-item-3" class="dropdown-menu"><a href="/page/radiographics/specialissues" class="dropdown-item">Monograph</a><a href="/topic/article-types/arttype-cookyjar?sortBy=Earliest" class="dropdown-item">Cases from the Cooky Jar</a><a href="/page/radiographics/visual-abstract" class="dropdown-item">Visual Abstracts</a><a href="/page/podcasts#radiographics" class="dropdown-item">Podcasts</a></div></div></li><li class="nav-item pr-xl-24"><div class="dropdown"><a id="publication-menu-item-4" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-small-bold">Authors/Reviewers</a><div aria-labelledby="publication-menu-item-4" class="dropdown-menu"><a href="/page/radiographics/rgauthor_instructions" class="dropdown-item">Instructions for Authors </a><a href="https://mc.manuscriptcentral.com/rg" class="dropdown-item">Submit a Manuscript </a><a href="/page/authorservices" class="dropdown-item">Author Services</a><a href="/page/radiographics/peer-review" class="dropdown-item">For Reviewers</a></div></div></li><li class="nav-item pr-xl-24"><div class="dropdown"><a id="publication-menu-item-5" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-small-bold">Core Learning</a><div aria-labelledby="publication-menu-item-5" class="dropdown-menu"><a href="/page/radiographics/rgteam/top10Home" class="dropdown-item">Top 10 Reading List</a><a href="/page/radiographics/abr-core-exam-study-guide" class="dropdown-item">ABR Core Exam Blueprints Article Index</a><a href="/page/radiographics/aapm-physics" class="dropdown-item">AAPM Physics Curriculum Article Index</a><a href="/page/radiographics/rgteam/top30_physics" class="dropdown-item">Top 30 Physics Articles</a><a href="/page/radiographics/nis" class="dropdown-item">Noninterpretive Skills Index</a><a href="/topic/presentations/fundamentals?sortBy=Earliest" class="dropdown-item">RadioGraphics Fundamentals</a><a href="/topic/presentations/RGTutorials?sortBy=Earliest&amp;startPage=&amp;SeriesKey=radiographics" class="dropdown-item">RadioGraphics Tutorials</a><a href="/page/radiographics/on-call" class="dropdown-item">On-Call Preparation Article Index</a><a href="/action/doSearch?target=digital-object-search&amp;DOResourceTypeId=exams&amp;sortBy=PubDateField_desc " class="dropdown-item">Test Your Knowledge Quizzes</a></div></div></li><li class="nav-item pr-xl-24"><div class="dropdown"><a id="publication-menu-item-6" href="#" role="button" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" class="nav-link dropdown-toggle text-small-bold">Browse by</a><div aria-labelledby="publication-menu-item-6" class="dropdown-menu"><a href="https://chatbot-beta.rsna.org" class="dropdown-item">RadioGraphics AI Research Assistant</a><a href="/topic/subspecialty/ai?sortBy=Earliest&amp;startPage=&amp;SeriesKey=radiographics" class="dropdown-item">AI</a><a href="/topic/subspecialty/bq?sortBy=Earliest&amp;startPage=&amp;SeriesKey=radiographics" class="dropdown-item">Biomarkers/Quantitative Imaging</a><a href="/topic/subspecialty/br?sortBy=Earliest&amp;startPage=&amp;SeriesKey=radiographics" class="dropdown-item">Breast Imaging</a><a href="/topic/subspecialty/ca?sortBy=Earliest&amp;startPage=&amp;SeriesKey=radiographics" class="dropdown-item">Cardiac Radiology</a><a href="/topic/subspecialty/ch?sortBy=Earliest&amp;startPage=&amp;SeriesKey=radiographics" class="dropdown-item">Chest Radiology</a><a href="/topic/subspecialty/ct?sortBy=Earliest&amp;startPage=&amp;SeriesKey=radiographics" class="dropdown-it